* {{Citation |first1=S.A. |last1=Torchinsky |display-authors=etal. |year=2013 |chapter=Characterization and Initial Results with EMBRACE |title=Proceedings of the Annual meeting of the French Society of Astronomy and Astrophysics |pages=439 |editors=L. Cambrésy, F. Martins, E. Nuss and A. Palacios |url= http://satorchi.net/skads/2013sf2a.conf..0439T.pdf |bibcode=2013sf2a.conf..439T}}

